/******************************************************************************************/
/*									*/
/*	Name:		EditValue						*/
/*	Description:	Routine to edit the value of a field.			*/
/*	Called by:	EditLine						*/
/*	Parameters:	String containing the name of the field and the value	*/
/*			separated by a tab.					*/
